**GraphQL 컨벤션**:
- Service: `@GrpcClient("user-grpc")`로 gRPC 호출
- Controller: `@Controller` + `@QueryMapping`/`@MutationMapping`
- 인증: `@PreAuthorize("hasAuthority('User'")`
- 사용자 ID: `@UserId userId: String` (커스텀 어노테이션)

### 4. 팔로우 기능 관련 코드 구조

#### 4.1 Proto 정의 위치
```
protobuf/src/main/proto/user/follow.proto
```

**Proto 컨벤션** (`grpc-skill` 참조):
```protobuf
syntax = "proto3";
package user;

service FollowService {
  rpc FollowUser(FollowRequest) returns (FollowResponse);
  rpc UnfollowUser(UnfollowRequest) returns (UnfollowResponse);
  rpc GetFollowers(GetFollowersRequest) returns (GetFollowersResponse);
  rpc GetFollowings(GetFollowingsRequest) returns (GetFollowingsResponse);
}

message FollowRequest {
  string user_id = 1;      # 요청자 ID
  string target_user_id = 2; # 팔로우 대상 ID
}

message FollowResponse {
  bool success = 1;
  string follower_id = 2;
  string following_id = 3;
  string created_at = 4;
}
```

**Proto 빌드**:
```bash
./gradlew :protobuf:clean :protobuf:build
```

#### 4.2 Entity 설계

**FollowEntity** (user → user 관계)
```kotlin
@Entity
@Table(catalog = "maum", name = "follow")
class FollowEntity(
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
    val id: String = "",

    @Column(nullable = false)
    val followerId: String,  # 팔로우하는 사람

    @Column(nullable = false)
    val followingId: String, # 팔로우 대상

    @CreatedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

    @LastModifiedDate
    var updatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),
)
```

**FollowRepository**:
```kotlin
interface FollowRepository : JpaRepository<FollowEntity, String> {
    fun findByFollowerId(followerId: String): List<FollowEntity>
    fun findByFollowingId(followingId: String): List<FollowEntity>
    fun findByFollowerIdAndFollowingId(followerId: String, followingId: String): FollowEntity?
    fun deleteByFollowerIdAndFollowingId(followerId: String, followingId: String)
}
```

#### 4.3 Service 구현

**FollowService** (비즈니스 로직)
```kotlin
@Service
class FollowService(
    private val followRepository: FollowRepository,
) {
    @Transactional
    fun followUser(followerId: String, followingId: String): FollowEntity {
        // 중복 확인
        followRepository.findByFollowerIdAndFollowingId(followerId, followingId)
            ?.let { throw AlreadyFollowingException() }

        return followRepository.save(
            FollowEntity(followerId = followerId, followingId = followingId)
        )
    }

    @Transactional
    fun unfollowUser(followerId: String, followingId: String) {
        followRepository.deleteByFollowerIdAndFollowingId(followerId, followingId)
    }

    @Transactional(readOnly = true)
    fun getFollowings(userId: String): List<FollowEntity> {
        return followRepository.findByFollowerId(userId)
    }

    @Transactional(readOnly = true)
    fun getFollowers(userId: String): List<FollowEntity> {
        return followRepository.findByFollowingId(userId)
    }
}
```

#### 4.4 gRPC Service

**FollowGrpcService** (user 모듈)
```kotlin
@GrpcService
class FollowGrpcService(
    private val followService: FollowService,
) : FollowServiceGrpc.FollowServiceImplBase() {

    override fun followUser(
        request: FollowRequest,
        responseObserver: StreamObserver<FollowResponse>,
    ) {
        try {
            val entity = followService.followUser(request.userId, request.targetUserId)
            val response = FollowResponse.newBuilder()
                .setSuccess(true)
                .setFollowerId(entity.followerId)
                .setFollowingId(entity.followingId)
                .setCreatedAt(entity.createdAt.toString())
                .build()
            responseObserver.onNext(response)
            responseObserver.onCompleted()
        } catch (e: AlreadyFollowingException) {
            responseObserver.onError(
                Status.ALREADY_EXISTS
                    .withDescription(e.message)
                    .asRuntimeException()
            )
        } catch (e: Exception) {
            responseObserver.onError(
                Status.INTERNAL
                    .withDescription("Internal error")
                    .asRuntimeException()
            )
        }
    }
}
```

#### 4.5 GraphQL API

**Schema** (`graphql/src/main/resources/graphql/follow.graphqls`)
```graphql
type User {
    id: ID!
    name: String!
    followersCount: Int!
    followingsCount: Int!
}

type FollowRelation {
    id: ID!
    followerId: ID!
    followingId: ID!
    createdAt: String!
}

extend type Query {
    myFollowings(limit: Int, offset: Int): [User!]!
    myFollowers(limit: Int, offset: Int): [User!]!
    isFollowing(targetUserId: ID!): Boolean!
}

extend type Mutation {
    followUser(targetUserId: ID!): FollowRelation!
    unfollowUser(targetUserId: ID!): Boolean!
}
```

**GraphQL Service** (graphql/service)
```kotlin
@Service
class UserService {
    @GrpcClient("user-grpc")
    private lateinit var followStub: FollowServiceGrpc.FollowServiceBlockingStub

    fun followUser(userId: String, targetUserId: String): FollowResponse {
        val request = FollowRequest.newBuilder()
            .setUserId(userId)
            .setTargetUserId(targetUserId)
            .build()
        return try {
            followStub.followUser(request)
        } catch (e: StatusRuntimeException) {
            throw CustomGraphQLException(e.trailers!!, e.status.description)
        }
    }
}
```

**GraphQL Controller** (graphql/controller)
```kotlin
@Controller
class UserController(
    private val userService: UserService,
) {
    @MutationMapping
    @PreAuthorize("hasAuthority('User')")
    fun followUser(
        @UserId userId: String,
        @Argument targetUserId: String,
    ): FollowRelation {
        val response = userService.followUser(userId, targetUserId)
        return response.toGraphQLResponse()
    }

    @QueryMapping
    @PreAuthorize("hasAuthority('User')")
    fun myFollowings(
        @UserId userId: String,
        @Argument limit: Int?,
        @Argument offset: Int?,
    ): List<User> {
        // 여러 서비스 호출 조합
        return userService.getFollowings(userId, limit ?: 20, offset ?: 0)
    }
}
```

